 "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/3/a/3afe7891-09d5-470e-aa41-71d89249875b.jpg?1782712627", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/ori/110/necromantic-summons?utm_source=api", "local": "img/necromancer/2f921740-de98-4276-8196-47a38a1e4591.jpg"}, {"id": "17455491-c295-4130-99b4-1b5c6ac1cd25", "name": "Young Necromancer", "set": "MH2", "type_line": "Creature — Human Warlock", "rarity": "uncommon", "colors": ["B"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/8/4/84b5f6da-5e0f-4cce-92fe-7aa69124e265.jpg?1782704670", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/8/4/84b5f6da-5e0f-4cce-92fe-7aa69124e265.jpg?1782704670", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/mh2/110/young-necromancer?utm_source=api", "local": "img/necromancer/17455491-c295-4130-99b4-1b5c6ac1cd25.jpg"}, {"id": "6494e3c4-5489-44a5-94b6-4ee2d7830896", "name": "Boneclad Necromancer", "set": "M20", "type_line": "Creature — Human Wizard", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["B"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/a/b/ab9ed2b9-5fb9-4633-8c9a-0594ae7c49c7.jpg?1782708327", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/a/b/ab9ed2b9-5fb9-4633-8c9a-0594ae7c49c7.jpg?1782708327", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/m20/93/boneclad-necromancer?utm_source=api", "local": "img/necromancer/6494e3c4-5489-44a5-94b6-4ee2d7830896.jpg"}, {"id": "2f72f111-450a-4da2-81fd-cbc4f9c1ef9d", "name": "Necromancer's Assistant", "set": "M15", "type_line": "Creature — Zombie", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["B"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/8/b/8b6a8b3e-2709-4036-838b-56cc82b0d917.jpg?1782713216", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/8/b/8b6a8b3e-2709-4036-838b-56cc82b0d917.jpg?1782713216", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/m15/107/necromancers-assistant?utm_source=api", "local": "img/necromancer/2f72f111-450a-4da2-81fd-cbc4f9c1ef9d.jpg"}, {"id": "dffa7c06-096a-47f8-9645-1ba7306ba5b0", "name": "Necromancer's Magemark", "set": "GPT", "type_line": "Enchantment — Aura", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["B"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/3/b/3b045121-7742-41ee-be27-591692f42331.jpg?1782717308", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/3/b/3b045121-7742-41ee-be27-591692f42331.jpg?1782717308", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/gpt/53/necromancers-magemark?utm_source=api", "local": "img/necromancer/dffa7c06-096a-47f8-9645-1ba7306ba5b0.jpg"}, {"id": "494895db-3da1-4a19-b7a5-ea47817f4e4f", "name": "Necromantic Thirst", "set": "CNS", "type_line": "Enchantment — Aura", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["B"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/8/c/8c934b09-726a-49c7-88fa-8b2e7ebf87b7.jpg?1782713304", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/8/c/8c934b09-726a-49c7-88fa-8b2e7ebf87b7.jpg?1782713304", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/cns/119/necromantic-thirst?utm_source=api", "local": "img/necromancer/494895db-3da1-4a19-b7a5-ea47817f4e4f.jpg"}], "flavor_snippets": [{"card": "Refurbished Familiar", "set": "MH3", "html": "When her beloved pet died, the artificer turned to <mark>necromancy</mark>.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/3/b338e078-629c-4cac-bd1d-e1f0a132728d.jpg?1782691313"}, {"card": "Minotaur Abomination", "set": "M14", "html": "&quot;Look at that. Shuffling, wobbling, entrails placed haphazardly. It&#x27;s shameful. Who would let that kind of work flap about for all to see?&quot;\n—Lestin, <mark>necromancer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/9/d/9dca75a1-443d-4f8e-b12b-2aada3a8e3e4.jpg?1782713936"}, {"card": "Cemetery Recruitment", "set": "FDN", "html": "To a <mark>necromancer</mark> as powerful as Liliana Vess, a graveyard is as good as a garrison of soldiers awaiting her command.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/3/4/34a80873-86d7-44a9-894b-65e8f77dd2ea.jpg?1782688815"}, {"card": "Doomed Necromancer", "set": "AFC", "html": "Many <mark>necromancers</mark> share the same last words—the ones that conclude the undeath ritual.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/d/2d3225e8-9902-4826-9cb3-68ecfaebb1e9.jpg?1782704145"}, {"card": "Undead Minotaur", "set": "M14", "html": "&quot;The work that went into creating this magnificent specimen. Horrific, deadly, well-balanced. Not all <mark>necromancers</mark> do elegant work like this.&quot;\n—Lestin, <mark>necromancer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/5/e/5e5ae910-ee1d-4958-92d9-0b06872913c6.jpg?1782713931"}, {"card": "Chilling Shade", "set": "CSP", "html": "Rimewind <mark>necromancers</mark> caught travelers in mystical blizzards then trapped their spirits in the mist of their final frozen breaths.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/d/0/d050c8b9-2b5a-4025-9886-73c418f4e22f.jpg?1782717071"}, {"card": "Dungeon Crawler", "set": "AFR", "html": "&quot;I think of it as giving them another chance to achieve their potential.&quot;\n—Nestus Wrasse, <mark>necromancer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/4/1/4138b66d-cf18-42a5-8522-241bd3969624.jpg?1782704383"}, {"card": "Stir the Grave", "set": "BOK", "html": "&quot;Your lungs may not draw breath, but while your hands can grip a sword, you will be useful to me.&quot;\n—Nighteyes, nezumi <mark>necromancer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/2/7287f68f-f2e2-4e6f-a772-29a629bb9ccd.jpg?1782718098"}, {"card": "Necromancer's Assistant", "set": "M15", "html": "Zombies and <mark>necromancers</mark> agree: easy access to brains is preferred.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/8/b/8b6a8b3e-2709-4036-838b-56cc82b0d917.jpg?1782713216"}, {"card": "Geomancer's Gambit", "set": "MH1", "html": "Telepathy changes minds, <mark>necromancy</mark> changes lives, but geomancy changes the world.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/3/23b67031-76b8-4511-a6dc-433d9450496e.jpg?1782708481"}, {"card": "Exotic Curse", "set": "DDE", "html": "Fouler than a <mark>necromancer</mark>&#x27;s kiss.\n—Jamuraan expression", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/e/1eff81c4-c402-437d-aace-dfe875d9857d.jpg?1782753180"}, {"card": "Drudge Reavers", "set": "TSP", "html": "&quot;The surface of the land is blanched with salt, but the soil beneath is reddened with death—a fertile ground for <mark>necromancy</mark>.&quot;\n—Lim-Dûl the <mark>Necromancer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/0/3/03c07d9a-afed-4028-9fa1-ec439b60f08f.jpg?1782716897"}, {"card": "Caged Zombie", "set": "M21", "html": "&quot;Six consecutive life sentences&quot; takes on a new meaning when <mark>necromancy</mark> is involved.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/f/8/f8067745-35b6-4abd-9ae9-712159a26c89.jpg?1782706957"}, {"card": "Fleshbag Marauder", "set": "CLU", "html": "Grixis is a world where the only things found in abundance are death and decay. Corpses, whole or in part, are the standard currency among <mark>necromancers</mark> and demons.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/f/c/fce2baa4-2976-4bbd-b6c5-a5a3c6a901be.jpg?1782693534"}], "mechanics_snippets": [{"card": "Necromancy", "set": "MKC", "html": "When this enchantment enters, if it&#x27;s on the battlefield, it becomes an Aura with &quot;enchant creature put onto the battlefield with <mark>Necromancy</mark>.&quot; Put target creature card from a graveyard onto the battlefield under your control and attach this enchantment to it. When this enchantment leaves the battlefield, that creature&#x27;s controller sacrifices it."}, {"card": "Necromantic Selection", "set": "TDC", "html": "Destroy all creatures, then return a creature card put into a graveyard this way to the battlefield under your control. It&#x27;s a black Zombie in addition to its other colors and types. Exile <mark>Necromantic</mark> Selection."}], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/3/b338e078-629c-4cac-bd1d-e1f0a132728d.jpg?1782691313", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/b/3/b338e078-629c-4cac-bd1d-e1f0a132728d.jpg?1782691313", "card": "Refurbished Familiar"}}